Text:
Season 3, Episode 4: What I Am

Original Air Date: 12 October 2006

Denny's father (Fred Ward)visits Izzie and gives something that will change everything. Meanwhile, Meredith needs an appendicitis and while she's high on morphine she has a talk with Addison for the first time since Addison found the panties. Mark "McSteamy" starts working at the hospital and Alex wants to work under him instead of Addison because Mark has a burnt face victim. And while Callie and George break up, Meredith finally picks one man.
